      <odd id="aspace_1d78aea66b8a2cd6d302a78c48076fbe">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 46-B (YRG 46-B), Records and materials documenting individual Yale buildings, facilities, and grounds.</p>  
      </odd>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_854a6ba825df61d85c1728594082d9f0">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The records were a gift of Roth and Moore Architects, 2006; awards transferred from Yale Seeley G. Mudd Library, 2015.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_13ec4e813fb09c930ccd915dce151b92">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>The materials are open for research.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
      <userestrict id="aspace_60ed6eec2f212097302f42ec12ef99de">
         <head>Conditions Governing Use</head>
         <p>Copyright has not been transferred to Yale University.</p>  
      </userestrict>
      <prefercite id="aspace_5dcde3cd5568ab3e48c3fa28cf055f4e">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Roth and Moore Architects Records Concerning the Seeley G. Mudd Library, Yale University (RU 1019). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <arrangement id="aspace_c630c7cc5d8e2e4c3bbe6099dc14ada0">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged by accession, and thereunder alphabetically by topic and material type.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_37a2fe189640a264c61120678c868942">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of memoranda, correspondence, notes, drawings, specifications, and awards documenting Roth and Moore Architects' design and construction of the Seeley G. Mudd Library, Yale University.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
